<item>
            <title>[LU-159] lustre-diagnostics does not support Jira</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-159</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lustre-diagnostics is a nice tool MJMac wrote to quickly, easily and efficiently profile a lustre machine and collecting the results in a well defined format.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This tool currently supports attaching a machine profile to automatically to a Bugzilla bug id - but it cannot attach to Jira issues.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre-diagnostics should be improved to support Jira.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10495">LU-159</key>
            <summary>lustre-diagnostics does not support Jira</summary>
